      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Matthew 16:16",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". “The Lord’s Christ,” ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Luke 2:26",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". After the estranging speech at Capernaum our Lord had asked, “Will ye also go away?” and then St Peter’s answer had been “we have believed and recognised that thou art ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "the Holy One of God,”",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "John 6:69",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
